  "detailed_description": "Barricade is a wave-based zombie FPS with a 90s aesthetic. Use physics props to build barricades and defend against zombies. Balance building, shooting, and repairs while spending money on weapons, upgrades, and defenses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR DEFENSES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/d28e1945d429517d0964fee08b983614.poster.avif?t=1729598421\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/d28e1945d429517d0964fee08b983614.webm?t=1729598421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/d28e1945d429517d0964fee08b983614.mp4?t=1729598421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gather props you find in the map and nail them to the environment to build a barricade. You are given the freedom to place props how you see fit, without grid limitations.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RETRO GUN PLAY</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/99e6c5ca0b82477a474be46dc8e6bf17.poster.avif?t=1729598421\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/99e6c5ca0b82477a474be46dc8e6bf17.webm?t=1729598421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/99e6c5ca0b82477a474be46dc8e6bf17.mp4?t=1729598421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>No gimmicks, no reloading, no aim down sights. Just non stop retro gun play, each gun has it's own powerful alternate fire mode to unleash maximum carnage.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IMPROVE YOUR SURVIVAL WITH UPGRADES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/0af2c331253109e862f9c46410ada370.poster.avif?t=1729598421\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/0af2c331253109e862f9c46410ada370.webm?t=1729598421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/0af2c331253109e862f9c46410ada370.mp4?t=1729598421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Buy new weapons, replace destroyed props, upgrade your guns infinitely, and MORE. You will need to make choices between offense and defense every round!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLE LEVELS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/d0c2830d4e8d9cb8e573ca94fbdce931.poster.avif?t=1729598421\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/d0c2830d4e8d9cb8e573ca94fbdce931.webm?t=1729598421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006180/extras/d0c2830d4e8d9cb8e573ca94fbdce931.mp4?t=1729598421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>3 unique maps, each offering a different selection of props and defensible rooms, and layouts to challenge you.",
